<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/286821-i-think-it-was-too-long-and-drawn-out-as">I think it was too long and drawn out, as was the Goldfinch. Is this a trend?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_286821'><a id="like_count_community_question_286821" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/286821?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">19 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F20821087-the-paying-guests">like</a></span>

